Privacy Policy

We appreciate your choice to use the Notifeel application and would like to clarify our commitment to protecting your privacy and the security of your personal information. Please read the following privacy policy carefully to understand how we collect, use, and protect your information.

1. Information Collection:
   When using the application, we may collect some personal information, including:

   a. Registration Information: When creating an account in our application, we may ask you to provide some personal information such as name, age, gender, and email.

   b. Geolocation Information: We collect your geolocation information using location-based technologies, even when the application is closed. This information is used to enhance your experience and provide location-based services.

   c. Device Information: We collect technical information about your device, such as browser type, operating system, and IP address for analytical purposes, performance improvement, and service delivery.

1. Information Usage:
   We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

   a. Service Provision: We use your information to provide and manage our services, including displaying profiles, offering search functionality, and sending notifications.

   b. Service Improvement: We analyze the information to understand how the application is used and improve it for a better user experience.

   c. Communication with You: We may use your information to communicate with you regarding service updates, promotions, and other relevant notifications.

1. Information Sharing:
   We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties without your consent, except in the following cases:

   a. With Your Consent: If you share your personal information with third parties for a specific purpose, we will use it according to the agreed-upon terms.

   b. Legal Compliance: If there are legal requirements or a legal request issued against us, we may disclose your information as per the privacy policy.

